READ SCENARIOS
1.  List Products 
    Fetch products with various filters and sorting options
    Lookup Key : category.name, rating.average, createdAt, price, quantity
    API : GET /products?category=Shirt&sort=rating&min_price=50&max_price=200&in_stock=true
    DB Query : find({ "category.name": "Shirt", price: { $gte: 50, $lte: 200 }, quantity: { $gt: 0 } }).sort({ "rating.average": -1 })
    Read heavy

2.  Search Products (Keyword Search)
    Query products by name, description, category using text search
    Lookup Key : name, description, category.name (text search)
    API : GET /products/search?keyword=shirt
    DB Query : find({ $text: { $search: "shirt" } }) or find({ name: /shirt/i, description: /shirt/i })
    Read heavy

3.  Get Product by ID
    Fetch single product with full details
    Lookup Key : _id
    API : GET /products/{productId}
    DB Query : findOne({ _id: <> })
    Read heavy

4.  Admin Dashboard: Product List
    Admin viewing list of all products
    Lookup Key : seller_id, createdAt
    API : GET /admin/products
    DB Query : find({}).sort({ createdAt: -1 })
    Not Read heavy


WRITE SCENARIOS
1.  Add New Product
    Create new product
    API : POST /products
    Write heavy

2.  Update Product 
    Update simple fields: name, description, image, category, price
    API : PUT /products/{productId}
    Not Write heavy

3.  Delete Product
    Soft delete or hard delete product
    API : DELETE /products/{productId}
    Not Write heavy

4.  Bulk Update Products (Admin)
    Update multiple products at once
    API : PUT /admin/products/bulk
    Write heavy


INDEX
db.products.createIndex({ "category.name": 1 }) //  category browsing
db.products.createIndex({ name: "text", description: "text", "category.name": "text" }) // Text search functionality
db.products.createIndex({ "category.name": 1, "rating.average": -1, price: 1 }) // Composite: covers category + rating sort + price filter (most list queries)
db.products.createIndex({ seller_id: 1, createdAt: -1 }) // Seller operations + admin dashboard